OL,5, A medical school in Japan has been     
OL,6, ordered to pay compensation to 13 women
OL,7, for discriminating against them in     
OL,8, entrance exams.                        
OL,10,FJuntendo University in Tokyo set       
OL,11,Fstricter requirements for female       
OL,12,Fstudents because it said women had     
OL,13,Fbetter communication skills than men   
OL,14,Fand had an advantage in interviews.    
OL,16,FThe judge ruled the requirements were  
OL,17,Fdiscriminatory, local media report.    
OL,19,FIt is believed to be the first ruling  
OL,20,Fof its kind in Japan.                  
